<h1>About The Java Toolbox</h1>

<p>The Java Toolbox is a collection of libraries, plug-ins and tools useful for Java development.</p>

<p>The goal of this site is to help Java developers discover and compare various projects for particular functionality.</p>

<p>This site aims to be as useful to the Java community as <a href="https://www.ruby-toolbox.com">The Ruby Toolbox</a> is to the Ruby/Rails community.</p>

<h2>Source Code</h2>

<p>This site is written using <a href="http://projects.spring.io/spring-boot/">Spring Boot</a> and the source code is available on GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/TheJavaToolbox/java-toolbox">https://github.com/TheJavaToolbox/java-toolbox</a>.</p>

